edu.temple.owlcis.service

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.temple.owlcis.service.User
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Advisor, Member, Moderator

    public abstract class User
extends Object
    User serves as the base class for all User role subtypes (Member, Advisor, and Moderator). The subtypes inherits all common properties and methods from this class, but it cannot be instantiated by itself. Common properties include fname, lname, id, and email. Common methods include access checkers for subtype privileges.
    Author:
    Lam
